data.description: Come see this beautiful ranch style home in a nice, quiet, and well-established neighborhood! Close to local schools, a fitness center, a park, and the new library, this home is in the perfect location! Enjoy the mature trees and spacious backyard with a shop (with power)! Recently remodeled, the inside is spacious and unique with endless possibilities! Come check it out today!  ***$8000 Paint/remodel allowance provided by seller with acceptable offer so you can personalize and make it your own!***
